{"tid":1731841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[技術討論] 見到隔離Post有人建議咁樣運物資　是否可行!!??","createTime":"2019-11-17T19:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T20:42:43.000Z","uid":122197,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e6dc4ce30b366760b7662b68c151e5ef1856a055","tid":1731841,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ae4fxE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ae4fxE.png&h=207bfe1c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇落真係好科幻, 但物理上又似乎可行!! 重要係, 要有人有無人機 + 去到理大附近較高 (只要高過理大就得) 既建築物。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講, 就係去到理大附近建築物 (高過理大), 拎一條繩 (要好長，幾百米長)，將繩既一端綁係固定物上 (e.g. 柱)，然後用無人機將繩既另一端運去理大，綁係理大任何固定物上。跟住將物資由建築物，透過繩運去理大。"},{"pid":"b5f6aa750bbafa1b94f3c00388cb1c381ef1a0d7","tid":1731841,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1118 跨界別大三罷 <br />\n集中post</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaZORQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaZORQ.jpg&h=81e84770&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUjcpqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUjcpqb.jpg&h=200794cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91bc2efebee722e9166297a71e77e506e1ce4ed4","tid":1731841,"uid":330673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:24.000Z","msg":"幫我推上去 好時機沖poly<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f92423559cedf227d50fba8341f41a1d69a7d73","tid":1731841,"uid":124618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:38.000Z","msg":"推！！！聽朝唔好塞交通住！ ！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731664\" data-